## Step 2: Preview Stream {#preview_stream type=preview required=false config=devices/preview.yaml}

Use this step to preview the RTSP stream in the platform UI.

### Wiring

1. Ensure the Jetson app is already running from Step 1.
2. Enter RTSP URL in this step.
3. Click **Connect**.

### Deployment Complete

1. Live stream is visible in the preview window.
2. You can disconnect and reconnect without redeploying Step 1.

### Troubleshooting

| Issue | Solution |
|-------|----------|
| Preview black screen | Verify RTSP URL with VLC/ffplay first |
| Connection timeout | Confirm RTSP port is reachable from this machine |
| ffmpeg not found | Install ffmpeg on the machine running this platform |

